<p>部分描述取自<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mortos" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1705184); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1705184&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610251938" alt="Mortos" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1705184)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mortos" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1705184); return false;">Mortos</a></span>创作的<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/forum/t-2266505/scp-4494">SCP-4494</a><br />
本文遵循CC-BY-SA 3.0</p>
